snippet.title: Betrayed - Official Announcement Trailer  | OTK Games Expo 2024
snippet.description:
Betrayed is a rag-doll party-shooter developed by Almost Good Games. Players will traverse diverse maps equipped with proximity chat to prove their innocence, act in deceptive ways, or create chaos. Betrayed is coming soon to PC with a Steam demo available now.

#Gaming #Games #GameTrailers
